{"tid":291801,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「我是中國人」概念 林鄭：幼兒起培養","createTime":"2017-06-21T00:47:13.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-21T16:26:42.000Z","uid":6181,"like":3,"dislike":58,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"aa90d49d8c2289b4fb15a57adbec9ee6f5c09883","tid":291801,"uid":6181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T00:47:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://skypost.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/1840310/%E3%80%8C%E6%88%91%E6%98%AF%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E4%BA%BA%E3%80%8D%E6%A6%82%E5%BF%B5%20%E6%9E%97%E9%84%AD%EF%BC%9A%E5%B9%BC%E5%85%92%E8%B5%B7%E5%9F%B9%E9%A4%8A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fskypost.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Farticle%2F1840310%2F%25E3%2580%258C%25E6%2588%2591%25E6%2598%25AF%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E3%2580%258D%25E6%25A6%2582%25E5%25BF%25B5%2520%25E6%259E%2597%25E9%2584%25AD%25EF%25BC%259A%25E5%25B9%25BC%25E5%2585%2592%25E8%25B5%25B7%25E5%259F%25B9%25E9%25A4%258A&d=CpdBlFin1w%2F29JcLDvXN%2BwRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=7e96a681\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://skypost.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/1840310/%E3%80%8C%E6%88%91%E6%98%AF%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E4%BA%BA%E3%80%8D%E6%A6%82%E5%BF%B5%20%E6%9E%97%E9%84%AD%EF%BC%9A%E5%B9%BC%E5%85%92%E8%B5%B7%E5%9F%B9%E9%A4%8A</a><br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥強調港府要做好教育，杜絕港獨侵害少年兒童。（新華社資料圖片）<br />\n<br />\n新政府即將上場，候任特首林鄭月娥接受中央媒體訪問時表示，大部分港人都不認為港獨是可考慮的方案，政府未來會對所有港獨行為嚴格執法，又指要讓孩子有國民身份認同，在幼兒階段就培養「我是中國人」的概念，初中則要將中史納入必修科目。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥接受新華社等中央媒體訪問時表示，接到中央任命書時感到任重道遠，又指一國兩制的初心和原意包含香港是國家不可分離的一部分，強調所有港獨行為都違反本地法律，未來會嚴格執法。<br />\n<br />\n痴撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/21/084707_b7077a5b518b7887b8522a629811c435.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F21%2F084707_b7077a5b518b7887b8522a629811c435.jpg&h=6b7190b6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"18b55fed66cba6ce41d330847360c441d6b5a910","tid":291801,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T00:47:51.000Z","msg":"叫佢陷家愛國先啦"},{"pid":"6ac5475428d8fda6e5f9ade8a9ea82dd9f502c15","tid":291801,"uid":2054,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T00:48:14.000Z","msg":"冚家英國人教人做中國人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8764664be20a5bfec9de72aa08ec8899e8ff58ce","tid":291801,"uid":6181,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T00:51:14.000Z","msg":"香港人未代<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"894226701728dac13252569f68a35828f26f647f","tid":291801,"uid":38523,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T00:51:18.000Z","msg":"但自己個仔就係英國培養<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04b77509d985b04d7458e05cdbfd03ff2472b052","tid":291801,"uid":6181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T00:53:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>但自己個仔就係英國培養<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n呢個女人真係好恐怖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe63e68583167b3a0d07a5b288511e3a4a4de3ab","tid":291801,"uid":41394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T00:53:41.000Z","msg":"上代種既因  果由下一代受<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52b32951aa4df1bb9f915f4a48bc66f4a029118b","tid":291801,"uid":46737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T00:56:06.000Z","msg":"不如以後所有新生嬰兒都要係手臂熨我是中國人"},{"pid":"6ab83559877ddfb9d8dea3901d99133427c1041c","tid":291801,"uid":6181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T00:57:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{